citations:
    citation-agot-catelyn-x:
        source: source-agot
        properties:
            locator: "Catelyn X"
            text_from_source: "A mob of men followed him up the slope, dirty and dented and grinning, with Theon and the Greatjon at their head. Between them they dragged Ser Jaime Lannister. They threw him down in front of her horse."
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "The Battle of the Whispering Wood. Robb Stark's forces ambush and destroy Jaime Lannister's cavalry column near Riverrun. Jaime is captured after cutting his way toward Robb and killing Torrhen Karstark, Eddard Karstark, and Daryn Hornwood. Grey Wind played a major role terrifying the Lannister horses."
